import React from 'react';
import { 
    FooterContainer, 
    FooterWrapper, 
    FooterNews,
    Footerh1,
    FooterSubs,
    FooterInp,
    FooterBtn,
    FooterP,
} from './style';


const Footer = () => {
    return (
        <>
        <FooterContainer>
            <FooterWrapper>
                <FooterNews>
                    <Footerh1>Newsletter</Footerh1>
                    <FooterSubs>
                        <FooterInp placeholder="Name"></FooterInp>
                        <FooterInp placeholder="E-mail address"></FooterInp>
                        <FooterBtn>Subscribe</FooterBtn>
                    </FooterSubs>
                    <FooterP>Be the first to know what's new at Ripin and get exclusive offers.</FooterP>
                </FooterNews>
                <FooterTitle>
                    <Footerh1>Sup</Footerh1>

                </FooterTitle>
            </FooterWrapper>
        </FooterContainer>
        </>
    )
}

export default Footer
